---
/**
 * ai-agents/0003 · Figure 1 — "How Claude Code Actually Works" (M4 architecture).
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from docs/ai-agents/lessons/0003-how-coding-agents-work.html
 * (figure + svg + figcaption). It lives as an .astro component, NOT inline in the
 * MDX, because MDX's JSX parser is unreliable with raw inline SVG that uses
 * kebab-case attributes (text-anchor, font-size, stroke-width, marker-end, …) and
 * self-referential marker ids. In an .astro file the SVG is plain HTML, so it
 * renders byte-for-byte. The marker-end url(#arw…) ids reference the shared
 * <defs> arrowheads emitted once in the MDX body (mirrors the source DOM).
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 620 240"
        role="img"
        aria-label="Claude Code architecture diagram showing User flowing down through Claude Code Runtime to Claude LLM, which fans out to four tool boxes, with a loop-back arrow from Claude LLM to Runtime"
    >
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <!-- User box -->
            <rect
                x="230"
                y="10"
                width="160"
                height="38"
                rx="6"
                fill="#fff"
                stroke="#d8d4c8"
                stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
            <text x="310" y="33" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" fill="#111110">User</text>

            <!-- Arrow User -> Runtime -->
            <line
                x1="310"
                y1="48"
                x2="310"
                y2="68"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>

            <!-- Claude Code Runtime box -->
            <rect
                x="150"
                y="70"
                width="320"
                height="42"
                rx="6"
                fill="#f1eee2"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
            <text
                x="310"
                y="88"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="13"
                fill="#111110"
                font-weight="600">Claude Code Runtime</text
            >
            <text x="310" y="103" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#6b675f"
                >orchestrates the agent loop</text
            >

            <!-- Arrow Runtime -> LLM -->
            <line
                x1="310"
                y1="112"
                x2="310"
                y2="132"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>

            <!-- Claude LLM box -->
            <rect
                x="200"
                y="134"
                width="220"
                height="38"
                rx="6"
                fill="#f1eee2"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
            <text
                x="310"
                y="157"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="13"
                fill="#111110"
                font-weight="600">Claude LLM</text
            >

            <!-- Dashed loop-back arrow: Claude LLM -> Runtime -->
            <path
                d="M 420 153 C 520 153 540 91 470 91"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.3"
                stroke-dasharray="4 3"
                fill="none"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></path>
            <text x="510" y="122" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
                >tool result</text
            >

            <!-- Plan file small box -->
            <rect
                x="530"
                y="70"
                width="80"
                height="32"
                rx="5"
                fill="#fff"
                stroke="#d8d4c8"
                stroke-width="1"
                stroke-dasharray="4 3"></rect>
            <text x="570" y="84" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f">Plan file</text>
            <text x="570" y="96" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f">(optional)</text>
            <line
                x1="470"
                y1="86"
                x2="530"
                y2="86"
                stroke="#d8d4c8"
                stroke-width="1"
                stroke-dasharray="3 3"></line>

            <!-- Fan-out arrows from LLM to tools -->
            <line
                x1="250"
                y1="172"
                x2="80"
                y2="200"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.3"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <line
                x1="280"
                y1="172"
                x2="210"
                y2="200"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.3"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <line
                x1="340"
                y1="172"
                x2="370"
                y2="200"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.3"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <line
                x1="370"
                y1="172"
                x2="510"
                y2="200"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.3"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>

            <!-- Tool boxes -->
            <rect
                x="20"
                y="202"
                width="120"
                height="34"
                rx="5"
                fill="#eef5ee"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                stroke-width="1.3"></rect>
            <text x="80" y="220" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#111110"
                >Read / Write</text
            >
            <text x="80" y="231" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#111110">Files</text>

            <rect
                x="155"
                y="202"
                width="100"
                height="34"
                rx="5"
                fill="#eef5ee"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                stroke-width="1.3"></rect>
            <text x="205" y="216" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#111110">Git</text>
            <text x="205" y="229" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#6b675f"
                >commit, diff, log</text
            >

            <rect
                x="310"
                y="202"
                width="120"
                height="34"
                rx="5"
                fill="#eef5ee"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                stroke-width="1.3"></rect>
            <text x="370" y="218" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#111110">Terminal</text>
            <text x="370" y="231" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#6b675f">(Bash)</text>

            <rect
                x="450"
                y="202"
                width="120"
                height="34"
                rx="5"
                fill="#eef5ee"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                stroke-width="1.3"></rect>
            <text x="510" y="218" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#111110">MCP</text>
            <text x="510" y="231" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#6b675f">Servers</text>
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        Claude Code = Claude (the LLM) + a runtime that exposes filesystem, git, terminal, and MCP
        as tools. The loop runs until Claude returns a final answer.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
